      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">Why One Agent Will Never Be Enough</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">The first instinct when deploying AI agents is to build one super-agent that does everything. It never works. The same way one employee cannot run your entire company, one agent cannot either. The future belongs to agent teams.</p>
